      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in stunning, like-new condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
