      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a concours-level E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S65 4.0L V8, distinguished by its eight individual throttle bodies and a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. Torque is managed via the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M-differential lock for optimized power delivery. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing precision damping across all drive modes. This vehicle has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing, ensuring mechanical longevity. The factory finish is flawless, and the interior retains its original matte texture with zero bolster compression. A truly turn-key enthusiast machine with a documented service dossier.",
